<p><a name="Spectrum-analyzer_functions" id="Spectrum-analyzer_functions"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Spectrum_analyzer&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1" title="Edit section: Spectrum-analyzer functions">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Spectrum-analyzer functions</span></h2>
<p>Certain functions and basic control---</p>
<p><a name="Frequency" id="Frequency"></a></p>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Spectrum_analyzer&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2" title="Edit section: Frequency">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Frequency</span></h3>
<p>Allows one to fix the window of frequencies to visualize in the screen.</p>
<p><a name="Marker.2Fpeak_search" id="Marker.2Fpeak_search"></a></p>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Spectrum_analyzer&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3" title="Edit section: Marker/peak search">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Marker/peak search</span></h3>
<p>Controls the position and function of markers and indicates the value of power.</p>
<p><a name="Bandwidth.2Faverage" id="Bandwidth.2Faverage"></a></p>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Spectrum_analyzer&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4" title="Edit section: Bandwidth/average">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Bandwidth/average</span></h3>
<p>Is a filter of resolution. The spectrum analyzer captures the measure on having displaced a filter of small bandwidth along the window of frequencies.</p>
<p><a name="Amplitude" id="Amplitude"></a></p>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Spectrum_analyzer&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5" title="Edit section: Amplitude">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Amplitude</span></h3>
<p>Is the maximum value of a signal in a point.</p>
<p><a name="View.2Ftrace" id="View.2Ftrace"></a></p>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Spectrum_analyzer&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6" title="Edit section: View/trace">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">View/trace</span></h3>
<p>Manages parameters of measurement. It stores the maximum values in each frequency and a solved measurement to compare it.</p>
<p><a name="Operation" id="Operation"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Spectrum_analyzer&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7" title="Edit section: Operation">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Operation</span></h2>
<table class="metadata plainlinks ambox ambox-content" style="">
<tr>
<td class="mbox-image">
