</div>
<div class="thumbcaption">
<div class="magnify"><a href="/wiki/File:My_Songo_Real_Time_Analysis.ogg" class="internal" title="Enlarge"><img src="/skins-1.5/common/images/magnify-clip.png" width="15" height="11" alt="" /></a></div>
